<div class="card content-card">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>This Attendance App is designed to help track attendance records locally. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>Data Collection</h2>
    <p>We collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>User names and email addresses (if provided)</li>
        <li>Attendance records including date, time, and status</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All data is stored locally on the server and is not shared with third parties. Data may be lost during server restarts or redeployments on free hosting tiers.</p>

    <h2>Data Usage</h2>
    <p>Your data is used solely for:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Tracking attendance records</li>
        <li>Generating attendance reports</li>
        <li>Identifying users within the system</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement reasonable security measures to protect your data. However, please note that no system is completely secure.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your attendance records</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Update your information</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy or your data, please contact the system administrator.</p>
</div>
